  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "OPAL is an administration layer for Policy Engines such as <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.openpolicyagent.org/\">Open Policy Agent (OPA)</a>, and <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/permitio/cedar-agent\">AWS' Cedar Agent</a> detecting changes to both policy and policy data in realtime and pushing live updates to your agents. OPAL brings open-policy up to the speed needed by live applications.",
